{"tid":143034,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"求貓狗嫌棄劑推薦","createTime":"2017-03-04T09:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T22:25:54.000Z","uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9af0394c5c40e9798c9041214027509c2c24e9e2","tid":143034,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T09:48:57.000Z","msg":"屋企隻貓亂柯屎尿左一段時間 <br />\n已經試過幾種方法<br />\n1.日日清貓沙 &gt; 情況持續<br />\n2.換更大嘅貓沙盤 &gt; 冇用<br />\n3.索尿入砂盤 &gt; he don't give a shit<br />\n4.見佢去廁所就讚 亂柯就罵 &gt; 彩我都傻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n別無辦法之下只好考慮最後手段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貓狗嫌棄劑 有冇巴絲有試過同樣情況"},{"pid":"46d9276ae2fc4085e16b8dd76d85ebb44f19d6d6","tid":143034,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T09:54:04.000Z","msg":"補番少少資料<br />\n<br />\n男 2歲近3歲 已閹（一歲前）<br />\n冇轉過擺位 冇換過貓沙牌子 冇搬過屋<br />\n呢間屋已經住左一年有多 一直冇事<br />\n換過貓糧 楓葉》Orijen 但係換之前已經亂柯緊"},{"pid":"3aaaa77fcb0e321596ec37244e6b7cd295afb210","tid":143034,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T10:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d958fd3fba6da9c1bb10569cd3bd388c35e29bc9","tid":143034,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T10:10:17.000Z","msg":"其他代替品都得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6285078a411de4e47a9ab6872325632506002ec","tid":143034,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T10:28:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 1"},{"pid":"7cd613bc2964aa1372b6cb9ff530acbbf5d0d5af","tid":143034,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T10:32:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其他代替品都得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有d天然既係橙皮/香草整成 但未試過"},{"pid":"c291e524074a23f4afcfad77812297507966a815","tid":143034,"uid":28031,"like":0,